{"tid":756404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵內地業務高層捲貪污調查　昨日突然離職 被保安挾走","createTime":"2018-07-26T04:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T07:01:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02fbd5ae3848e63b1b65ae69994c77cea80b4bb1","tid":756404,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"港鐵一位負責內地事務的港鐵高層昨日（25日）突然離職，並在保安人員陪同下「執包袱」離開港鐵九龍灣總部辦公室。<br />\n兩名消息人士向《香港01》透露，港鐵一位負責內地業務的高層懷疑捲入貪污調查，被港鐵即時解僱。《香港01》已向港鐵查詢，正等待回覆。"},{"pid":"00cdee53ebb0300fec8e1acc6c2e39d1933efe16","tid":756404,"uid":126567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"炒人還炒人<br />\n整返個站先"},{"pid":"ece848b0df76650fde979a1c4799016fdc8c5ffb","tid":756404,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"係未諗住搵人祭旗就當無野"},{"pid":"062b5b16fe676ead9a9f020354b35de4079bbe0d","tid":756404,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"HK01話佢有份搞深圳天頌，呢個盤係2011年批至2015年賣樓<br />\n再對比返港鐵各年年報主要管理人員個表，再睇下而家港鐵物業發展(深圳)有限公司董事班友<br />\n發覺有條友何X華由2014係年報出現負責中國物業，去到2018年都仲係穩坐管理層一職<br />\n如果支那01咁報呢個高層出黎....<br />\n<br />\n2014年年報<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/images/investor/2014frpt/C127.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcorporate%2Fimages%2Finvestor%2F2014frpt%2FC127.pdf&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=58c64084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/images/investor/2014frpt/C127.pdf</a><br />\n2015年年報<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/annual2015/C127.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Farchive%2Fcorporate%2Fch%2Finvestor%2Fannual2015%2FC127.pdf&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4f42e407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/archive/corporate/ch/investor/annual